{"tid":834371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中秋望團圓】狗場主人10號風球重傷9天仍昏迷 妻泣訴：你幾時好返同我繼續行？","createTime":"2018-09-24T07:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T08:03:39.000Z","uid":73262,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb78b2817e735badace522fe17a9b7d3adcc03d","tid":834371,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"9月16日山竹襲港帶來無情的10號風球，把好心人洪家棣及太太辛苦經營的「老有所依」慈善動物安老院吹塌幾乎夷為平地，洪家棣更慘遭狂風吹起雜物擊傷致腦出血及骨折，他送院後已昏迷9天。堅強的洪太負擔起重建狗場及安置20多隻狗狗的重責，從未言倦，但今日是中秋節，當談到心愛的丈夫在病塌中的仍未蘇醒及未度過危險期，鐵娘子也不禁垂淚。洪太稱唯一的中秋願望便是丈夫可盡快奇蹟康復，與她繼續合力照顧早已視為親子女的愛犬，人狗齊吃月餅，一家<br />\n團圓。<br />\n記者謝頌昕 徐雲庭<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180924&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58718100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180924%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58718100&d=I351fSihAHQRxhP70sHOzHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c7c8117b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180924%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58718100&h=f1efd6ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180924&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58718100</a>"},{"pid":"dcc52e45cbf2806dbcf67cafc0fb9dba49f65f72","tid":834371,"uid":98386,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"好人冇好報又一實例 睇下林奠呢啲仆街 喺屋企笑尻打工仔狼狽返工之後仲死出黎講風涼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f398b78359ef218927d81def5beabbde0db43969","tid":834371,"uid":174207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"有錢出錢"},{"pid":"352636fa801a1c83f685ecfb6f107c3dd0c3dbb8","tid":834371,"uid":199120,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"好心冇好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb118f63361ed462c45f2af965fb9caadefb81e0","tid":834371,"uid":113000,"like":0,"disli